---
title: Cal Smart Tex-Mex Beef Bowls with Mexican Street Corn Slaw
description: Lightly charred corn adds a lovely, smoky quality to Mexican-inspired slaw on top of a wild rice medley. It's finished with Tex-Mex ground beef and cooling crema for a flavour-packed meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R1027_W29_CA_RT157675-1_Main_low-995d16c4.jpg
